  "prompt": "Which are the top software companies in Ahmedabad for .net developers?",
  "response": "As of my last knowledge update in October 2023, several companies in Ahmedabad are known for hiring .NET developers and are recognized in the software industry. Here are some of the top software companies in Ahmedabad that often seek .NET talent:\n\n1. **TCS (Tata Consultancy Services)** - A major player in IT services, TCS has a strong presence in Ahmedabad and regularly hires .NET developers for various projects.\n\n2. **Infosys** - Another leading IT services company, Infosys has a significant presence in Ahmedabad and offers opportunities for .NET professionals.\n\n3. **Wipro** - Wipro also recruits .NET developers for various roles across its projects and services.\n\n4. **Accenture** - Known for consulting and professional services, Accenture employs .NET developers in its technology division.\n\n5. **Cognizant** - This multinational company offers IT services and consulting and has opportunities for .NET developers.\n\n6. **Fingent** - A technology consulting firm that specializes in custom software development and often hires .NET developers for various projects.\n\n7. **Hope Technologies** - A software development company that works on various technologies, including .NET.\n\n8. **Saviom** - Focused on project management solutions, Saviom often seeks skilled .NET developers.\n\n9. **Visionary RCM** - A healthcare outsourcing company that requires .NET developers for its software solutions.\n\n10. **Techno Infonet** - A web and mobile application development company that often recruits .NET developers.\n\n11. **Softonic Solutions** - A software development and consulting firm that works with various technologies, including .NET.\n\n12. **Mobiweb Technologies** - Specializing in mobile and web applications, they frequently hire .NET developers.\n\nPlease note that the status and hiring needs of these companies can change, so it's always a good idea to check their careers page or websites like LinkedIn for the most current job opportunities. Additionally, local startups and smaller firms often seek .NET developers, so exploring those options could also be beneficial.",
